<p>
It&#39;s time for my annual self review. It&#39;s been another weird year. <a href="https://simblob.blogspot.com/2021/12/what-i-did-in-2021.html" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">Last year I said</a> I was going to spend more time on experiments, art, and learning, and I would improve my existing guides.
</p>

